Package org.neo4j.internal.batchimport.store

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PrepareIdSequence
    Exists to allow IdSequence with specific behaviour relevant to import to be injected into CommonAbstractStore.prepareForCommit(AbstractBaseRecord, IdSequence, PageCursorTracer).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BatchingNeoStores
    Creator and accessor of NeoStores with some logic to provide very batch friendly services to the NeoStores when instantiating it.
    BatchingTokenRepository<RECORD extends TokenRecord>
    Batching version of a TokenStore where tokens can be created and retrieved, but only persisted to storage as part of flush.
    BatchingTokenRepository.BatchingLabelTokenRepository  
    BatchingTokenRepository.BatchingPropertyKeyTokenRepository  
    BatchingTokenRepository.BatchingRelationshipTypeTokenRepository  
    PageCacheFlusher
    A dedicated thread which constantly call PageCache.flushAndForce() until a call to PageCacheFlusher.halt() is made.
    SecondaryUnitPrepareIdSequence
    Assumes that records have been allocated such that there will be a free record, right after a given record, to place the secondary unit of that record.
    SecondaryUnitPrepareIdSequence.NeighbourIdSequence  
    StorePrepareIdSequence
